  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x153;Hadin Kai do min zaman lafiya&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x9D; (Uniting for Peace): Strengthening youth&#xE2;&#x20AC;&#x2122;s resilience to violent extremism in Borno State</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The specific objectives of the project are:&#xA0;1. To strengthen incentives for individuals at risk of recruitment to contribute constructively to their communities&#xA0;2. To reduce the appeal of joining violent extremist groups&#xA0;through promoting peaceful methods for addressing grievances</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The&#xA0;overall goal of the project is&#xA0;to&#xA0;reduce the risk of recruitment of&#xA0;community members by Boko Haram&#xA0;by engaging communities in prevention activities.</narrative>
  </description>
